scripts.comment: In this tutorial we will draw a circle with spheres. Follow the steps and try to make your own copy of the program. Hint: think of how many degrees the Beetle turns at every step if it wants to walk in the circle.

block.comment: This block moves the Beetle one unit forward, Try it!
This block places a sphere with a 0.5 diameter.

scripts.comment: Now try to snap the three blocks together.

block.comment: This is a repeat block. You can place other blocks inside.
The hat block runs your program.
This block clears the viewport area.

scripts.comment: Now write a program that draws a circle of spheres.

block.comment: This block rotates the Beetle by 15 degrees.
